description: It's an old habit. I spent my whole life trying not to be careless. Women and children can afford to be careless, but not men. Mr Corleone is Johnny Fontane's godfather.
title: Test Action 1

description: What's the matter with you, huh? What am I going to do? Am I going to make that baby an orphan before he's born? If anything in this life is certain, if history has taught us anything, it is that you can kill anyone. I don't feel I have to wipe everybody out, Tom. Just my enemies. Te salut, Don Corleone.
title: Test Action 2

description: You can act like a man! It's a Sicilian message. It means Luca Brasi sleeps with the fishes. I have a sentimental weakness for my children and I spoil them, as you can see. They talk when they should listen. Do me this favor. I won't forget it. Ask your friends in the neighborhood about me. They'll tell you I know how to return a favor. Don't you know that I would use all of my power to prevent something like that from happening?
title: Test Action 3
